Package: fastfit
Type: Package
Title: Fast and Convenient Regression Workflows and Visualizations
Version: 0.7.8
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Paul H.", family = "McClelland", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "PaulHMcClelland@protonmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3119-6531")))
Maintainer: Paul H. McClelland <PaulHMcClelland@protonmail.com>
Description: Fast and lightweight statistical modeling toolkit built on data.table for 
    rapid generation of publication-ready tables and figures. Includes descriptive statistics
    with group comparisons, univariable and multivariable regression workflows, and flexible
    export to various formats. Also provides convenient visualizations for regression outputs 
    based on ggplot2.
